ZH: 我今天要去医院挂号看医生。
EN: I'm going to the hospital today to register and see the doctor.

ZH: 每次看医生都要先挂号。
EN: You have to register before seeing the doctor every time.

ZH: 挂号费用是多少？
EN: How much is the registration fee?

ZH: 请到窗口挂号。
EN: Please register at the counter.

ZH: 我已经挂号了，现在只等叫号。
EN: I've already registered, now I just have to wait for my turn.

ZH: 挂了号就可以去等候了。
EN: After registering, you can go wait.

ZH: 我提前挂了号，避免排队。
EN: I registered early to avoid waiting in line.

ZH: 这家医院的挂号系统很方便。
EN: The registration system in this hospital is very convenient.

ZH: 您需要提供身份证才能挂号。
EN: You need to provide your ID card in order to register.

ZH: 我忘记挂号了，只能再去排队了。
EN: I forgot to register, so I have to wait in line again.

ZH: 请您先到那边挂号。
EN: Please go over there to register first.

ZH: 到医院挂号的人很多，需要排队。
EN: There are many people registering at the hospital, you need to wait in line.

ZH: 挂号台在医院门口左侧。
EN: The registration desk is on the left side of the hospital entrance.

ZH: 医生不能接受未挂号的患者。
EN: Doctors cannot see patients who haven't registered.

ZH: 您需要在网上挂号才能预约看医生。
EN: You need to register online in order to make an appointment to see the doctor.

ZH: 请把挂号单交给护士。
EN: Please give the registration form to the nurse.

ZH: 您的挂号已经成功了。
EN: Your registration is successful.

ZH: 请在这里填写挂号信息。
EN: Please fill out the registration information here.

ZH: 挂号信息输入后点击确认。
EN: Click confirm after entering the registration information.

ZH: 明天早上请您准时来挂号。
EN: Please come to register on time tomorrow morning.
